&lt;p&gt;Once all villagers decided to pray for rain. &lt;br&gt;
On the day of prayer, all the people gathered, &lt;br&gt;
but only one boy came with an umbrella.    &lt;br&gt;
This is faith or innocence?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you throw babies in the air, &lt;br&gt;
they laugh because they know you will catch them.   &lt;br&gt;
This is trust or helplessness or ignorance?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
